ygData.subject: Good place to hunt for mid 40's through 51.
ygData.msgSnippet: I found this spot a while back, well I am sure I am not the only one to find it but you know what I mean.  Velkor s Labyrinth (sp?) is really good exp for mid
ygData.messageBody:
I found this spot a while back, well I am sure I am not the only one to find it but you know what I mean.  Velkor's Labyrinth (sp?) is really good exp for mid 40's to 52 at the zone in.  There are spiders that spawn at the zone must be 20 or more that you can pull without going too deep and getting to any of the traps.  The experience here was really well and the mobs kind of reminded me of LDC's (only their dot isn't nearly as bad, or it didn't seem so) as far as HP's went.  So they really didn't take too long to kill and they have some nice rare/random drops they also can drop gems for the Thur quest armor.  I got a silk something or other glove for pure caster it was 4ac 3int 35mana and some saves.  Well, talk more later.
 
Mu
